  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿伙计，我需要你的帮助。我需要巨量的能量来维持当前的活动，尤其是矿场，那个你曾经帮我修建的设施。通常我会找其他人订购燃料，但不幸的是，现在我联系不上供应商了。你知道现在哪里还有剩余的燃料吗？我觉得湾区会有一些东西。雇佣兵，你能帮我去检查一下吗？",
    "en": "Hey friend, I could use some help. It takes an incredible amount of energy to sustain my current activities, especially considering my farm, the one you helped me with resources for. I usually order fuel from other sources, but unfortunately, there is no way to contact the supplier at the moment. Do you think there are still unexhausted fuel tanks left somewhere? I think there should have been something left in the cape area. Can you check it out, mercenary?"
  },
